        "timestamp": "2017-08-04 00:21:03.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nThe following is not included in oparent. I just keep all distributionManagement to avoid regression\n      \n<site>\n       <id>ecomp-site</id>\n       <url>dav:${nexusproxy}${sitePath}</url>\n</site>",
